Posts.Content: Jan 28, 2010 12:36AM Aliting33 wrote: I am 24. This is actually my first post on this forum. I was diagnosed this month, January 18 with atypia (?), tubular carcinoma. I'm not sure yet what stage I'm in because I haven't had a formal discussion yet with my doctor. I had my first bilateral MRI and a painful mammogram yesterday. I also had an ultrasound and tomorrow I'm going in for genetic testing. I will be seeing my surgeon tomorrow so she can give me more details. I will make sure to return to this topic with updates.
